  <refentry id="function.cpdf-set-text-matrix">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>cpdf_set_text_matrix</refname>
    <refpurpose>Sets the text matrix</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>bool</type><methodname>cpdf_set_text_matrix</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>pdf_document</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>array</type><parameter>matrix</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     The <function>cpdf_set_text_matrix</function> function sets
     a <parameter>matrix</parameter> which describes a transformation 
     applied on the current text font. &return.success;
    </para>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

